LEEDS--Gerard. UJA-Federation of New York mourns the passing of Gerard Leeds, a dedicated philanthropist committed to helping Holocaust survivors, as well as the entire Jewish community, and founder of the Institute for Student Achievement, Inc. We extend our heartfelt condolences to Gerard's wife, Lilo; his children, Michael (Andrea), Daniel (Sunita), Richard (Anne), Greg (Maria), and Jennifer Leeds; his grandchildren; and the entire family. Alisa R. Doctoroff, President; Linda Mirels, Chair of the Board; Eric S. Goldstein, CEO 1/3